ign<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2987fc48 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"2987fc48\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1afed8b6\" data-id=\"1afed8b6\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-36d30361 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"36d30361\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-13b4fcdd\" data-id=\"13b4fcdd\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div data-split-settings=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;chars&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp2&quot;}\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f4f21fb wavo-headig-split heading-has-split-yes wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5f4f21fb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What is the Grid System?<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-54003dee wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"54003dee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">The <b>Grid System<\/b> has been helping artists of all kinds (including writers) for a long time. First used by a <b>13th century<\/b> artist, who fused it with the golden ratio, the grid system has been a super tried and trusted methodology for centuries.<br> \n<br>\n\u25cf <b>In writing<\/b> it allowed writers to place their handwriting neatly on paper; later, it became a universal standard in the publishing industry. <br>\n<br>\n\u25cf <b>In painting<\/b> it helped artists achieve better results and maintain greater consistency in their pieces.<br>\n<br>\n\u25cf <b>In cartography<\/b>, it was also essential to use the grid system to achieve the necessary accuracy in maps.<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-032269f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"032269f\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-84f7da3\" data-id=\"84f7da3\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8a55fca elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8a55fca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"wp-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"626\" height=\"417\" src=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/writing_example.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-6949\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/writing_example.jpg 626w, https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/writing_example-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption class=\"widget-image-caption wp-caption-text\">Writing<\/figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-f890b2f\" data-id=\"f890b2f\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-90f5d05 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"90f5d05\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"wp-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"626\" height=\"417\" src=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/painting_examplee.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-6948\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/painting_examplee.jpg 626w, https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/painting_examplee-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption class=\"widget-image-caption wp-caption-text\">Painting<\/figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-3ea9f04\" data-id=\"3ea9f04\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2b0b7f5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2b0b7f5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"wp-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"626\" height=\"417\" src=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/cartografia_example.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-6950\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/cartografia_example.jpg 626w, https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/cartografia_example-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption class=\"widget-image-caption wp-caption-text\">Cartography<\/figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-efe9490 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"efe9490\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-bb7edbc\" data-id=\"bb7edbc\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fea1371 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"fea1371\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">And we currently use it in <b>product design<\/b> to take advantage of that whole set of benefits, among others.\n<br><br>\nOkay, but... Here we've come to answer the next question:<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9be277c wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9be277c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><i>\u2014 \"Which is better: 8pt or 10pt?\"<\/i><\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c29b254 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c29b254\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Next we will analyze <b>the reasons<\/b> why the <b>8pt Grid is better<\/b> for product design.<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7f67650 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"7f67650\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div data-split-settings=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;chars&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp2&quot;}\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0e514f7 wavo-headig-split heading-has-split-yes wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0e514f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">1. Scales perfectly<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d0f6497 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d0f6497\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">As you may know, we design for the smallest screen size. This allows us to scale our assets to the different sizes required by the devices (@0.75 | @1 | @1.5 | @2 | @3 ...).\n<br><br>\nIn the following image you can see what happens with the first 3 scalings in both Grid Systems:<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-63fb92b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"63fb92b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"821\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/escalado_grids_en.svg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-7050\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32094b8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"32094b8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-f3bcf5f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"f3bcf5f\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-9dc794c\" data-id=\"9dc794c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div data-split-settings=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;chars&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp2&quot;}\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-62e4b62 wavo-headig-split heading-has-split-yes wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"62e4b62\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2. Apple and Google recommend it<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ad564ed wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ad564ed\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">If Apple is using an 8pt grid in its Design System (Human Interface) and Google also in theirs (Material Design), for us as product designers it has a lot of importance, especially if the product we are working on is an application to be used on mobile devices.\n<br><br>\nRemember that app is going to have to run on an <b>iOS or Android<\/b> device, yes or yes! \ud83d\ude42<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e940299 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e940299\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1080\" height=\"615\" src=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/android_vs_ioss.svg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-6953\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8e888b8 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8e888b8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">We must clarify that this does not force us in any way to work with 8pt, but we must take into account that we are designing a product that, in the end, will run on an operating system. Therefore, if the user opens our application and finds a <b>similar visual environment<\/b> (margins, sizes, paddings, etc) we will achieve a <b>great consistency<\/b>.<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-62eb372 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"62eb372\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-3467ec7\" data-id=\"3467ec7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5fd4a9c elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"5fd4a9c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div data-split-settings=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;chars&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp2&quot;}\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-528f860 wavo-headig-split heading-has-split-yes wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"528f860\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">3. Greater flexibility<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-29a3ae9 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"29a3ae9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">When we get down to work and we are designing our pixel perfect, we have to work constantly with margins, paddings and sizes ... and in many cases, the size jump that allows us a grid of 5px as a basic unit does not serve us, as it is too aggressive (especially in the first measures).\n<br><br>\n \u25cf In the following image I show you <b>how it works in 8pt:<\/b><\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8ea84e4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8ea84e4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"wp-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1049\" height=\"285\" src=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/saltos_grid_8_EN.svg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-7051\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption class=\"widget-image-caption wp-caption-text\">8pt and 4pt as basic units<\/figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a265455 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a265455\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">As you can see, that first part which I call <b>*First measures<\/b>, gives us a range of possibilities when designing, since many times we will need very small spacing between interface elements, and 5px would be excessive for these cases.\n<br><br>\nYou can also see that there is a <b>*2<\/b> there, and maybe you think it should not be there, but it is precisely for these specific cases where we can use it exceptionally and it will come in handy when <b>making the most of the screen space<\/b> is our priority.\n<br><br>\n \u25cf In the following image you can see how it works in 10pt, and so you will see better the difference:\n\nTranslated with www.DeepL.com\/Translator (free version)<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f92a962 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f92a962\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"wp-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1049\" height=\"285\" src=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/saltos_en_grid_10.svg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-6978\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption class=\"widget-image-caption wp-caption-text\">10pt and 5pt as basic units<\/figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2787050 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2787050\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">As you will see, here the flexibility is much less, since the jumps will be <b>at least 5px<\/b> and this in many elements of the interface will be excessive when we are designing.<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-5779eac elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"5779eac\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-cdfe42d\" data-id=\"cdfe42d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1bfe4c7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"1bfe4c7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f8b335 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2f8b335\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">\nI hope you found the article useful.\n<\/br><\/br><\/br>\nSee you in the next one! \ud83d\ude42<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-fcb5c05 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"fcb5c05\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-409e843\" data-id=\"409e843\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-38da990 premium-title-icon-row-reverse premium-title-color elementor-widget elementor-widget-premium-addon-title\" data-id=\"38da990\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"premium-addon-title.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"premium-title-container style7\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"premi